===現役機隊===
截至2022年4月，大韓航空機隊平均機齡為11年，並擁有以下飛機<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.koreanair.com/local/jp/gd/eng/au/of/au_of.jsp |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-06-02 |archive-date=2015-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626221235/https://www.koreanair.com/local/jp/gd/eng/au/of/au_of.jsp |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.planespotters.net/Airline/Korean-Air-Lines|title=Korean Air Lines Fleet Details and History|publisher=planespotters.net|accessdate=April 29, 2013|archive-date=2016-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160924041612/https://www.planespotters.net/airline/Korean-Air-Lines|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.koreanair.com/local/eu/gd/eng/au/of/au_of.jsp Korean Air official fleet page] {{Wayback|url=http://www.koreanair.com/local/eu/gd/eng/au/of/au_of.jsp |date=20150626215106 }}. Koreanair.com.</ref>：，所有機型均採用[[奇異航空|GE]]以及[[普惠公司|PW]]生產的發動機（若與韓亞航空確認合併收購後，A350-941以及A350-1041將是大韓航空首例採用勞斯萊斯特倫特系列發動機）
